;------------------------------------
; PuzzleBOBS audio configuration file
;------------------------------------
;
; Here you can configure PuzzleBOBS game audio's part. If you find a value in which is specified 
; the range between brackets you must respect its and consider that extremes values could be 
; included.
; If you don't find range you could insert a SIGNED LONG INT value from -2147483647
; to +2147483647. If you found (+) you must insert a positive value. 
; If you insert a string respect Amiga Dos directives and use and use quotes in strings with 
; spaces.
; If you put a 0 in place of a string you disable the sample or module.
; If an error occurs, PuzzleBOBS will confirm it to you. 
;
; Have a good audio configuration.
;
; ------------------------
; Samples ConfigFile About
; ------------------------
;
; Here there is a block of string about samples ConfigFile's author. Each string can not go 
; over 79 chars of lenght.
;
"Kinnon (Mario Chisari)"	;Author of samples ConfigFile, if 0 is "unknown".
"E se penso all'allegria"		;Free comment 1.
"che mi da un'amica mia"		;Free comment 2.
"con i suoi vestiti bianchi" 	;Free comment 3.
"i suoi sorrisi colorati......"	;Free comment 4.
0		;Free comment 5.
0		;Free comment 6.
;
; -------------  
; Sample's path
; -------------
;
PuzzleBOBS:audio/Mario/Urto3.snd	;Sample used when is moved the bobs in the menu.
PuzzleBOBS:audio/Mario/Urto.snd		;Sample used when is selected a menu's voice.
;
;
PuzzleBOBS:audio/Mario/livello.snd	;When a bob is fired from the rotating pointer.
0									;When you press fire but is not possible to launch a bob.
PuzzleBOBS:audio/Mario/splash		;When a bob explodes.
PuzzleBOBS:audio/Mario/urto3.snd	;When a bob collides with lateral limits.
PuzzleBOBS:audio/Mario/urto2.snd	;When a bob collides with top limit.
PuzzleBOBS:audio/Mario/lancio3.snd	;When a bob collides against an other bob.
;
PuzzleBOBS:audio/Mario/clock1		;Time of autolaunch timer near pointer.
PuzzleBOBS:audio/Mario/urto3.snd	;When the beam lower down the level.
PuzzleBOBS:audio/Mario/3			;when you get an aim line.
0									;When the game is over.
